'''India Rising Series 2026''' or '''IRS 2026''' is a premium Battlegrounds Mobile India (BGMI) tournament IP powered by '''[https://www.krafton.com/en/ KRAFTON]''' and features a total prize pool of ₹10,00,000 {{Abbr/INR}}.

==About==
===Format===
''*Registrations: March 14th - 21st, 2026
* '''IN-Game Qualifiers:''''' Mar 27th - 29th, 2026
* '''Round 1:''''' Apr 3rd - 6th, 2026
** 512 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams divided into 32 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.<!--
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 32 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 256 Teams) qualify for ''Round 2.-->

* '''Round 2:''''' Apr 9th - 12th, 2026
** 256 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 16 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.<!--
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 4 Teams}} from each group (Total 64 Teams) qualify for ''Quarter Finals.-->

* '''Quarter Finals:''''' Apr 14th - 17th, 2026
** 64 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 32 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to ''Semi Finals.

* '''Semi Finals:''''' Apr 19th - 22nd, 2026
** 32 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Single Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} advance to ''Grand Finals.

* '''Grand Finals:''''' Apr 24th - 26th, 2026
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

